      %div{:id => 'products_mats_mops_towels_mats_row_container_right'}
        %p
          The “Laundry Friendly” anti-fatigue mat features a Closed-Cell Nitrile 
          Rubber construction that is completely launderable. The anti-microbial 
          treated, slip-resistant surface is grease, oil and chemical resistant. 
          Complete Comfort mats are available in 2x3 and 3x5 sizes. This 
          ergonomically superior anti-fatigue mat is available in 5/8” thickness.
        %p
          Provide us with your logo (preferably electronically) and we will 
          custom design a 
          %span{:class => 'blue'} Logomat 
          for your needs.  Using state of the art 
          technology, our logomats are the premium option for mat function 
          and image/brand enhancement.
